sequenceDiagram
    participant G as Guest
    participant B as Booking Orchestrator
    participant Cal as Calendar Svc
    participant Pay as Payment (Stripe)
    participant N as Notify Svc
    participant H as Host

    Note over G,H: Booking Saga: lock -> charge -> confirm -> notify
    G->>B: POST /book {listing, checkin, checkout}
    B->>B: validate dates, listing exists
    B->>Cal: lock dates (SQL txn)
    loop each night in range
        Cal->>Cal: SELECT FOR UPDATE row
        alt status = available
            Cal->>Cal: UPDATE status=booked
        else conflict
            Cal-X B: AVAILABILITY_LOST
        end
    end
    Cal-->>B: dates locked
    B->>Pay: authorize hold (escrow)
    alt payment OK
        Pay-->>B: auth_id
        B->>B: persist booking (CONFIRMED)
        B-->>G: 200 {booking_id}
        B-)N: send confirmations
        N-)H: new booking
        N-)G: receipt + check-in info
        Note over Pay: funds escrowed until 24h post check-in
    else payment fail
        Pay-X B: declined
        B->>Cal: compensate (release dates)
        B-->>G: 402 payment failed
    end
